{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Coven is a fast-paced retro fps/slasher where you take on the role of a young girl in an alternate 1600's who is wrongly accused of witchcraft and is burned at the stake. She's resurrected by an unknown force and seeks revenge. Her path of vengeance will take her across time and space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785940/extras/gif_coven_churchFight.gif?t=1730121255\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the first episode:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Utilize an explosive mix of early modern period weaponry and magic</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Movement is key -  dash, slide and slow down time in order to survive</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Eat the flesh of the newly deceased to regain health so you may continue on your path of rigorous vengeance</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Explore villages, temples, forests and different places in time to uncover the secrets of the old gods </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Soundtrack by John S. Weekley aka Primeval</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2 more episodes will release during early access which will continue the story. Each set in a different time and place across history.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"E1M1 Secrets","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1785940/885678a6eeaf4cab2ac38816283d7044375e259f.jpg"},{"name":"E1M1b Secrets","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1785940/b4a938134d97866de2fb2829d1833970166e3113.jpg"},{"name":"E1M2 Secrets","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1785940/b9fa5f9f5f528a89003de9611f07476c12228f65.jpg"},{"name":"E1M3 Secrets","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1785940/61a7e29b6b49ab43d54ae7002db3883ed2dfcf02.jpg"},{"name